{
  "texts": [
    "The results indicated that ChatGPT is generally perceived positively with emotion of joy being the most prevalent.",
    "Since its inception, the positive perception has decreased slightly and in languages other than English.",
    "In the analysis of data specifically related to education, the number of papers that see ChatGPT as a threat is almost equal to the number of those who view it an opportunity.",
    "These authors also call for more research, particularly calling for investigating the perceptions from specific user groups.",
    "These three studies all provide an overarching perspective as to how all users perceive ChatGPT."
  ]
}